"{\"uid\": \"nytimes.com-athletic-5306494-2024-02-28-team-usa-paris-olympics-roster-devin-booker-jrue-holiday\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"NBA    As USA Basketball officials work to piece together the final roster of12 NBA stars headed to the Paris Olympicsthis summer, a picture is beginning to emerge of who will be on the team.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 191, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10, \"end\": 24, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Basketball\", \"score\": 0.9999999475380732, \"rank\": 5.246203441266014e-08, \"text\": \"USA Basketball\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Basketball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Basketball\"}, {\"begin\": 80, \"end\": 83, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0253233973900828e-20, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 104, \"end\": 109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999970468707, \"rank\": 2.9529271067865876e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In USA Basketball's recent discussions with stakeholders,Boston Celticsstar guard, Olympic gold medalist andNBAchampionJrue Holiday, andPhoenix SunsAll-NBA guard and Olympic gold winnerDevin Bookerare mentioned along withKevin Durant,LeBron James,Stephen Curry,Joel EmbiidandJayson Tatumas the expected core of the team barring injury, multiple NBA sources and sources close to the American team toldThe Athletic.\", \"from\": 193, \"to\": 606, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 427, \"end\": 439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LeBron James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}, {\"begin\": 440, \"end\": 453, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Curry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.08789176558543e-39, \"text\": \"Stephen Curry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Curry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Curry\"}, {\"begin\": 538, \"end\": 541, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0253233973900828e-20, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 575, \"end\": 583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_League\", \"score\": 0.7167425122824991, \"rank\": 0.3563727953219303, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6631808\", \"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement  At least some of these have already begun initial planning and public commitments related to their Olympic participation, sources said.\", \"from\": 608, \"to\": 758, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Multiple USA officials said Wednesday the final Olympic roster is not set.\", \"from\": 759, \"to\": 833, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 768, \"end\": 771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.6260204025940691, \"rank\": 0.5870600747881669, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition to the seven bona fide heavyweights listed above, budding superstarsAnthony EdwardsandTyrese Haliburton, two members of the USA's 2023 World Cup team, are under strong consideration for the Paris Games, those same sources said.\", \"from\": 837, \"to\": 1076, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 942, \"end\": 952, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haliburton_County\", \"score\": 0.9823811128536776, \"rank\": 0.017931580343703245, \"text\": \"Haliburton\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haliburton_County\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haliburton_County\"}, {\"begin\": 973, \"end\": 976, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.6260204025940691, \"rank\": 0.5870600747881669, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Edwards and Haliburton were two of the top players for the Americans last summer, on a team that finished a disappointing fourth at the World Cup in Manila.\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1233, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1089, \"end\": 1099, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haliburton_County\", \"score\": 0.9823811128536776, \"rank\": 0.017931580343703245, \"text\": \"Haliburton\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haliburton_County\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haliburton_County\"}, {\"begin\": 1226, \"end\": 1232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manila\", \"score\": 0.9960083446303467, \"rank\": 0.004007384142116615, \"text\": \"Manila\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manila\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manila\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If all nine of these players make the USA roster, there would be three players left to pick.\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1327, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1273, \"end\": 1276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.6260204025940691, \"rank\": 0.5870600747881669, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Only Embiid is a \\\"traditional\\\" big man (in the modern sense of the position - he shots 37 percent from 3-point range as a 7-footer), so the Americans would need to add more size.\", \"from\": 1328, \"to\": 1506, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TheMiami Heat'sBam AdebayoandLos Angeles Lakers'Anthony Davisare considered strong candidates for the roster as well, and Davis said during All-Star weekend that he would play for the Americans if asked.\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1710, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"James, who is 6-foot-8 and still runs the floor like a freight train on offense but weighs more than 260 pounds, could also play the 4 in a lineup with Durant and/or Tatum on the wings.\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1897, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1712, \"end\": 1717, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 0.9999999308961403, \"rank\": 6.904651442550853e-08, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team USA, the four-time-defending Olympic gold medalist in men's basketball, has a target date of sometimein the early rounds of the NBA playoffs to announce its Paris roster, which means late April or May.\", \"from\": 1899, \"to\": 2105, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1899, \"end\": 1907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999720574276129, \"rank\": 2.7941998451154392e-05, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2032, \"end\": 2035, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0253233973900828e-20, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 2061, \"end\": 2066, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999970468707, \"rank\": 2.9529271067865876e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is still a major caveat for any player considered a lock - that player's health at the time of the announcement and then when training camp begins in early July.\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2273, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a major reason why, last month, the American team put out a list of 41 players from which the final team will be picked.\", \"from\": 2274, \"to\": 2399, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2315, \"end\": 2323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_League\", \"score\": 0.7167425122824991, \"rank\": 0.3563727953219303, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6631808\", \"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If someone gets hurt or bows out, Team USA will have been able to stay engaged with potential replacements.\", \"from\": 2400, \"to\": 2507, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2434, \"end\": 2442, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999720574276129, \"rank\": 2.7941998451154392e-05, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"GO DEEPER  The Lille Olympics: How badminton bumped NBA, WNBA stars from Paris' first week  USA officials - led by managing director Grant Hill and Sean Ford, who oversees day-to-day operations for the men's national team, and coach Steve Kerr - are still counting on Embiid, who underwent surgery to repair a meniscus tear earlier this month but could return to the76ers'lineup before the end of the regular season.\", \"from\": 2509, \"to\": 2925, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2561, \"end\": 2564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0253233973900828e-20, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 2566, \"end\": 2570, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 0.9999999065480595, \"rank\": 9.345202012850677e-08, \"text\": \"WNBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 2582, \"end\": 2587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999970468707, \"rank\": 2.9529271067865876e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2601, \"end\": 2604, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.6260204025940691, \"rank\": 0.5870600747881669, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2642, \"end\": 2652, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grant_Hill\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.343062123510029e-32, \"text\": \"Grant Hill\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grant_Hill\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grant_Hill\"}, {\"begin\": 2657, \"end\": 2661, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sean_Astin\", \"score\": 0.5348797513652939, \"rank\": 0.6485059699973539, \"text\": \"Sean\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sean_Astin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sean_Astin\"}, {\"begin\": 2662, \"end\": 2666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ford_Motor_Company\", \"score\": 0.9998953053475613, \"rank\": 0.00010470185987216788, \"text\": \"Ford\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ford_Motor_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ford_Motor_Company\"}, {\"begin\": 2742, \"end\": 2752, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Kerr\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Steve Kerr\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Kerr\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Kerr\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Embiid's plans to represent Team USA in theOlympicsremain intact, a source said.\", \"from\": 2926, \"to\": 3006, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2954, \"end\": 2962, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999720574276129, \"rank\": 2.7941998451154392e-05, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement  Decorated American Olympic veterans Durant and James have been emphatic publicly in their commitment to the Paris Olympics, and USAB simply could not keep them off the team if they want to play.\", \"from\": 3008, \"to\": 3217, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3070, \"end\": 3075, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 0.9999999308961403, \"rank\": 6.904651442550853e-08, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Curry, who has never played in an Olympics, wants this year and team (coached by Kerr, his longtime coach on theWarriors) to be his debut.\", \"from\": 3218, \"to\": 3356, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Team USA has been pursuing Holiday for much of the NBA season, and Holiday has delivered his commitment to USAB officials in recent weeks, sources said.\", \"from\": 3358, \"to\": 3510, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3358, \"end\": 3366, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999720574276129, \"rank\": 2.7941998451154392e-05, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3409, \"end\": 3412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0253233973900828e-20, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team officials have valued Holiday's two-way ability, point-of-attack defense and dynamic playmaking.\", \"from\": 3511, \"to\": 3612, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Holiday was considered Team USA's second-most important player behind Durant at the Tokyo Games in 2021.\", \"from\": 3613, \"to\": 3717, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3636, \"end\": 3644, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999720574276129, \"rank\": 2.7941998451154392e-05, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The draw to determine who the Americans will play in the opening round of the Olympic tournament in Lille, France, is March 19.\", \"from\": 3719, \"to\": 3846, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3819, \"end\": 3824, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille_OSC\", \"score\": 0.9999975339740952, \"rank\": 2.4660320758510633e-06, \"text\": \"Lille\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille_OSC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille_OSC\"}, {\"begin\": 3826, \"end\": 3832, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9562998595145212, \"rank\": 0.045655426536337015, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"GetThe Bounce, a daily NBA Newsletter from Zach Harper and Shams Charania, in your inbox every morning.Sign up here.\", \"from\": 3848, \"to\": 3964, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3855, \"end\": 3861, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tower_Records\", \"score\": 0.9993948911233426, \"rank\": 0.0006054752551034826, \"text\": \"Bounce\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tower_Records\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tower_Records\"}, {\"begin\": 3871, \"end\": 3874, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0253233973900828e-20, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Photo: Winslow Townson / USA Today)  Spot the pattern.\", \"from\": 3966, \"to\": 4021, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Connect the terms  Find the hidden link between sports terms  Play today's puzzle  Joe Vardonis a senior NBA writer for The Athletic, based in Cleveland.Follow Joe on Twitter@joevardon\", \"from\": 4022, \"to\": 4206, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4105, \"end\": 4108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\", \"score\": 0.9690164811033339, \"rank\": 0.03197414884125711, \"text\": \"Joe\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\"}, {\"begin\": 4127, \"end\": 4130, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0253233973900828e-20, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 4142, \"end\": 4154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Athletic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Athletic\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Athletic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Athletic\"}, {\"begin\": 4189, \"end\": 4196, \"title\":